Classification<br>
7. C.M. Bishop: Neural Networks for Pattern Recognition<br>
8. T. Hastie, R. Tibshirani, J.H, Friedman: The Elements of<br>
Statistical Learning<br>
9. B.D. Ripley: Pattern Recognition and Neural Networks</span></h2>

